entries.question: Show the name and the release year of the song by the youngest singer.
entries.predicted_sql: SELECT T1.Name, T1.Song_release_year FROM singer AS T1 JOIN singer_in_concert AS T2 ON T1.Singer_ID = T2.Singer_ID JOIN concert AS T3 ON T2.concert_ID = T3.concert_ID WHERE T1.Age = (SELECT MIN(T1.Age) FROM singer AS T1)
entries.gold_sql: SELECT song_name ,  song_release_year FROM singer ORDER BY age LIMIT 1
entries.llm_response:
SELECT T1.Name, T1.Song_release_year

JOIN concert AS T3 ON T2.concert_ID = T3.concert_ID 
WHERE T1.Age = (SELECT MIN(T1.Age) FROM singer AS T1)
